cs.PL, cs.LO, cs.SE, cs.AI, cs.DS

This paper deals with operational semantics of pure Prolog, which falls under the category of programming languages (cs.PL). The paper also discusses a constructive version of variant lemma for implemented Horn clause logic, which is related to logic (cs.LO). The concept of prenaming introduced in the paper can be useful in software engineering (cs.SE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) for handling variables. Finally, the paper also discusses an incremental approach for handling new variables, which is related to data structures (cs.DS).
